    {
      "id": "JHdujlbn6YVqCthWagIbF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 867.8594677036286,
      "y": 245.18124999999998,
      "width": 515.625,
      "height": 403.2,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 923991807,
      "version": 98,
      "versionNonce": 912358865,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773914227805,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "while ptr_i <= ptr_high:\n\nCase 0 : \n    swap => O(1)\n    ptr_low++\n    ptr_i++\n\nCase 1 : \n    nothing\n    ptr_i++\n\nCase 2 :\n    swap => O(1)\n    ptr_high--\n\n    \n                    O(n)\n\nEach element is processed at most once, and although \nthe pointer i may not always advance, the high pointer \ndecreases, ensuring the loop runs in linear time.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "while ptr_i <= ptr_high:\n\nCase 0 : \n    swap => O(1)\n    ptr_low++\n    ptr_i++\n\nCase 1 : \n    nothing\n    ptr_i++\n\nCase 2 :\n    swap => O(1)\n    ptr_high--\n\n    \n                    O(n)\n\nEach element is processed at most once, and although \nthe pointer i may not always advance, the high pointer \ndecreases, ensuring the loop runs in linear time."
    },
