      "updated": 1773913943700,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Usage:\n\nptr_low\nptr_i\nptr_high\n\nSo, 3 variables\n\n            O(1)\n\nThe algorithm uses constant extra space since \nit only relies on a few pointers and performs in-place swaps.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Usage:\n\nptr_low\nptr_i\nptr_high\n\nSo, 3 variables\n\n            O(1)\n\nThe algorithm uses constant extra space since \nit only relies on a few pointers and performs in-place swaps."
